@startuml
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/proveo-ca/identity/main/proveo.puml
title Autonomous Offensive Agent (sandboxed)
' Paper: LLM Agents can Autonomously Hack Websites, arXiv:2402.06664
' Paper: PentestGPT, USENIX Security 2024, arXiv:2308.06782
' Level: 4
' Provenance: domain: security (≈ omnigent sandbox / egress)

cloud     "LLM agent"                  as LLM  <<cloud>>
node      "Sandbox (egress-gated)"      as SBX  <<host>>
component "Recon → exploit tools"      as TOOL <<app>>
component "Target\n(authorized scope)"  as TGT  <<error>>

LLM  ARROW_CLOUD TOOL : plan + invoke
SBX  ARROW_MAIN  TOOL : contain
TOOL ARROW_ERROR TGT  : recon / exploit
TGT  ARROW_QUEUE LLM  : observation (loop)

note bottom of SBX
  An LLM agent runs recon/exploit **inside a sandbox with egress gating**
  (authorized scope only) — the offensive analog of the harness's
  sandbox + egress controls.
end note
@enduml
